2026-03-11  Vladimir Tsichevski  <Vladimir Tsichevski <vvt@goldencode.com>>

	* Author info extraction problems:

	-- there may be more than one author in the title-info element
	-- the author element in document-info may be broken

	Example:
	 <description>
  <title-info>
   <author>
    <first-name>Владимир</first-name>
    <middle-name>Иванович</middle-name>
    <last-name>Дмитревский</last-name>
   </author>
   <author>
    <first-name>Борис</first-name>
    <middle-name>Дмитриевич</middle-name>
    <last-name>Четвериков</last-name>
   </author>
  </title-info>
  <document-info>
   <author>
    <first-name>Alexx</first-name>
    <last-name></last-name>
   </author>
  </document-info>

	We have to:

	-- collect all <author> elements to autor list
	-- use the first author in the list to form the catalog name

